sequenceDiagram
%% ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
%% SEQUENCE — options quick-ref
%% ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
%% Header:       sequenceDiagram
%% Participants: participant id [as Label]  ·  actor id [as Label]
%% Arrows:       ->> · -->> · -> · --> · -x · --x · -) · --)
%% Activation:   + activate · - deactivate  (suffix on arrow line)
%% Overlays:     Note over id1,id2: text  ·  Note left of id: text  ·  Note right of id: text
%% Fragments:    alt/else · opt · loop · par/and · critical · break  (close with end)
%% Config:       autonumber
%% Frontmatter:  --- yaml block --- (before header)
%% Comments:     %% text  (stripped before parse — safe on any line)
%% ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Client as Web Client
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant DB as Database

    User->>+Client: Enter credentials
    Client->>+Auth: POST /login
    Auth->>+DB: Query user record
    DB-->>-Auth: User data + hash

    alt Valid credentials
        Auth-->>-Client: 200 JWT token
        Client-->>-User: Login successful
    else Invalid credentials
        Auth-->>Client: 401 Unauthorized
        Client-->>User: Show error message
    end

    loop Token refresh (every 15 min)
        Client->>Auth: POST /refresh
        Auth-->>Client: New JWT token
    end

    opt Access protected resource
        Client->>Auth: GET /api/data
        Auth-->>Client: 200 Protected data
    end

    Note over Auth,DB: All DB queries use TLS
